      "rationale": "The FEA software suite (Ansys Mechanical 2021 R2) is operated under a documented software quality assurance plan compliant with 21 CFR Part 11 and FDA guidance on computer software assurance. Version-controlled simulation scripts, regression test suites, and audit trails are maintained. Achieved Gradation 3 exceeds the required Gradation 2 for a medium model risk context."
